content: 10 million (Rio City Hall), 10 million (Rio State Government). Banco Itau, Heineken, Deezer and other brands are sponsors but covered other costs, the total event is said to have cost 50 million reais to hold. Meanwhile, thousands die every year due to the terrible healthcare system in the State of Rio de Janeiro.
